I decide to give up my knight for two pawns, giving me a mobile pawn center.   Fritz considers this a major blunder, since I am not only giving up material but Black will have the initiative for awhile.   My feeling is that Black's initiative will eventually dissipate and then my mobile pawn center will make it's power felt.   This is all beyond the machine's horizon and illustrates the difference in how humans view things as opposed to computers.
